      <p class="closing-line closing-vivid">It is symbiogenesis: code that thinks, intelligence that lives in Abjects, communication that heals itself. Programs, LLMs, and P2P identity merged into a single organism that no component could become alone.</p>
      <p class="closing-line closing-body">And it renders itself. An X11-style Canvas compositor where Abjects paint their own faces. No other agent framework has a visual body.</p>
